The,AviationData,Systems,Airports,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,global,airport,data,into,their,web,applications,The,API,mostly,focuses,on,airport,location,data,AviationData,Systems,hosts,data,on,more,than,airports,from,countries,and,all,continents,It,covers,both,large,international,airports,and,small,local,ones